            "type": "object",
            "$ref": "#/definitions/protoMemory"
          }
        }
      },
      "description": "ImportBatchRequest carries full-state rows (original timestamps, recall state, significance,\ngroup, event links) to be upserted by id into the store as-is - a data migration, not a fresh\nwrite. It is the ingest half of Transfer and is re-sendable: re-importing the same rows is\nidempotent."
    },
